---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = "Contact SEO Leeds | Get in Touch";
const description = "Contact SEO Leeds for a free consultation. Covering Leeds, West Yorkshire, and the Northern Powerhouse. Email or call to discuss your SEO needs.";

const schema = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 1,
        "name": "Home",
        "item": "https://seo-leeds.uk/"
      },
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": 2,
        "name": "Contact",
        "item": "https://seo-leeds.uk/contact/"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Contact SEO Leeds",
    "description": "Contact SEO Leeds for a free consultation. Covering Leeds, West Yorkshire, and the Northern Powerhouse.",
    "url": "https://seo-leeds.uk/contact/",
    "isPartOf": {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "SEO Leeds",
      "url": "https://seo-leeds.uk"
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How quickly will you respond to my enquiry?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "We respond to all enquiries within one working day, typically within a few hours during business hours. Initial consultations are scheduled within the same week where diary permits."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you offer free consultations?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. Every engagement starts with a free, no-obligation consultation. We will review your current search performance, discuss your commercial objectives, and outline what SEO can realistically achieve for your business before any commitment."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do I need to be based in Leeds to work with you?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No. While we specialise in Leeds and West Yorkshire SEO, we work with businesses across the Northern Powerhouse and nationally. Our consultancy is remote-first, so location is not a barrier. However, our deepest expertise is in the Leeds market and surrounding areas."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What information should I prepare before getting in touch?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Ideally, have your website URL, a rough idea of which services or products you want to rank for, and any existing Google Search Console or Analytics access you can share. However, none of this is required to start a conversation — we can work through the details together."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Base title={title} description={description} schema={schema}>
  <section class="px-4 py-12">
    <div class="prose">
      <h1>Contact SEO Leeds</h1>

      <p>SEO Leeds is a remote-first SEO consultancy covering Leeds, West Yorkshire, and the wider Northern Powerhouse region. Whether you are a professional services firm in the city centre, a restaurant in Headingley, or an e-commerce business shipping from South Bank, getting in touch is the first step toward understanding what organic search can do for your revenue.</p>

      <div class="quick-answer">
        <p><strong>Quick answer:</strong> Email <a href="mailto:2012.infinite@gmail.com">2012.infinite@gmail.com</a> for a free, no-obligation consultation. We respond within one working day. Every conversation starts with understanding your business — no hard sell, no jargon, no obligation.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>How to Get in Touch</h2>

      <p>The best way to reach us is by email. Send your enquiry to <a href="mailto:2012.infinite@gmail.com">2012.infinite@gmail.com</a> with a brief description of your business, your website URL, and what you are looking to achieve through SEO. We will respond within one working day with an initial assessment and suggested next steps.</p>

      <p>If you prefer, you can also outline your situation in as much or as little detail as you like. Some clients send a single sentence — "I need help with SEO for my Leeds business" — and we take it from there. Others provide detailed briefs with analytics access, competitor lists, and specific ranking targets. Both approaches work. The important thing is starting the conversation.</p>

      <p>Every enquiry receives a personal response from Sunny Patel, the SEO consultant behind SEO Leeds. You will not be passed to a junior account manager or assigned to a different team. The person you speak to at the start is the person who does the work.</p>

      <h2>Coverage Area</h2>

      <p>SEO Leeds provides <a href="/services/">SEO services</a> across the following areas:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Leeds city centre</strong> — including the financial district, Wellington Place, Park Square, East Parade, Victoria Quarter, Trinity Leeds, Leeds Dock, and South Bank</li>
        <li><strong>Leeds suburbs</strong> — Headingley, Chapel Allerton, Roundhay, Horsforth, Meanwood, Morley, Pudsey, Garforth, Rothwell, Wetherby, and all LS postcodes</li>
        <li><strong>West Yorkshire</strong> — Bradford, Wakefield, Huddersfield, Halifax, Dewsbury, and surrounding towns</li>
        <li><strong>Northern Powerhouse</strong> — York, Harrogate, Sheffield, Manchester, and the wider North of England for businesses seeking regional or national SEO</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Our consultancy is remote-first, which means we are not constrained by geography. We work with businesses across the UK. However, our deepest market knowledge, local connections, and competitive intelligence are in the Leeds and West Yorkshire region. If your business serves customers in Leeds, we understand the search landscape you are competing in better than any London-based agency parachuting into the Northern market. See our <a href="/areas/">area-specific pages</a> for more detail on how we approach individual Leeds suburbs and districts.</p>

      <h2>What to Expect</h2>

      <p>After you get in touch, here is what happens:</p>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>Initial conversation.</strong> We will arrange a call or video meeting to understand your business, your goals, and your current search performance. This takes 20-30 minutes and is completely free. There is no pitch deck, no hard sell — just a practical discussion about where you are and where you want to be.</li>
        <li><strong>Preliminary assessment.</strong> Based on our conversation, we will provide an initial view of your SEO situation: what is working, what is not, and where the biggest opportunities lie. For many businesses, we can identify quick wins and structural issues from a brief review of your site and Google Search Console data.</li>
        <li><strong>Proposal.</strong> If there is a fit, we will put together a clear proposal outlining the recommended scope, timeline, deliverables, and <a href="/seo-pricing-leeds/">pricing</a>. No lock-in contracts, no hidden fees, no ambiguous retainer scopes. You will know exactly what you are getting and what it costs before committing.</li>
        <li><strong>Decision on your timeline.</strong> There is no pressure to proceed immediately. Some clients start the same week. Others take a month to evaluate their options. We are available when you are ready.</li>
      </ol>

      <p>If you want to get a head start before our conversation, request a <a href="/free-seo-audit-leeds/">free SEO audit</a> and we will send you an initial analysis of your website's search health.</p>

      <h2>Find Us</h2>

      <p>SEO Leeds operates as a remote-first consultancy covering the Leeds metropolitan area and beyond. The map below shows our primary coverage area in Leeds city centre.</p>

      <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d37832.77925989498!2d-1.5767!3d53.7997!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x48795c6c42ec2a79%3A0x444aa3eae68b3e8!2sLeeds!5e0!3m2!1sen!2suk!4v1" width="100%" height="400" style="border:0;" loading="lazy" title="SEO Leeds coverage area - Leeds city centre map"></iframe>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How quickly will you respond to my enquiry?</h3>
        <p>We respond to all enquiries within one working day, typically within a few hours during business hours. Initial consultations are scheduled within the same week where diary permits.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you offer free consultations?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Every engagement starts with a free, no-obligation consultation. We will review your current search performance, discuss your commercial objectives, and outline what SEO can realistically achieve for your business before any commitment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do I need to be based in Leeds to work with you?</h3>
        <p>No. While we specialise in Leeds and West Yorkshire SEO, we work with businesses across the Northern Powerhouse and nationally. Our consultancy is remote-first, so location is not a barrier. However, our deepest expertise is in the Leeds market and surrounding areas.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What information should I prepare before getting in touch?</h3>
        <p>Ideally, have your website URL, a rough idea of which <a href="/services/">services</a> or products you want to rank for, and any existing Google Search Console or Analytics access you can share. However, none of this is required to start a conversation — we can work through the details together during the initial consultation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2 style="color: white; margin-top: 0;">Ready to Talk SEO?</h2>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:2012.infinite@gmail.com" style="color: var(--color-accent);">2012.infinite@gmail.com</a> for a free consultation. No obligation, no jargon — just a clear conversation about what SEO can do for your Leeds business.</p>
        <a href="mailto:2012.infinite@gmail.com">Send an Email</a>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;"><a href="/">Home</a> | <a href="/services/">Services</a> | <a href="/about/">About</a> | <a href="/seo-pricing-leeds/">Pricing</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
